Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我告诉你们  这两个乡巴佬被禁飞了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}'Cause let me tell you, those farm boys are grounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:22.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  长官  决不允许拿军用飞机冒险\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir, an entirely unacceptable use... of m-m-military aircraft, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-拿我的帽子来  -是的  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Get my hat. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,叫这些亡命徒去杜立特办公室\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get those hedge-hoppers in Doolittle's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,已经训练两年了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}After two years of training...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们以为造价四万五千美元的战斗机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you believe that a $45,000 airplane...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是用来玩吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is there for your amusement?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不是  长官  我只是磨练技巧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, sir. I was just trying... to keep my edge, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上礼拜你玩空中翻筋斗\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And when you did the outside loop last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也是为了磨练技巧吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}what did you think that was? Honing your skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那不是飞行技巧!麦考利  是哗众取宠!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's not training, McCawley. That's a stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:48.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也是愚蠢和不负责的行为\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I personally consider it to be reckless... and irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,少校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,怎么会啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How could that be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你可是那招\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when you're famous for being the first man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,的开山鼻祖\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in the world ever to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别跟我耍嘴皮子\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't get cute with me, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没有耍嘴皮子  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, sir, I don't mean to be disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请恕我直言  我只是认为\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just think that... well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果仅仅只是为了出风头  这是愚蠢和不负责的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is reckless and irresponsible if you're just doing it to be a show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我这样是为了启发战友\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I was doing it to try to inspire the men, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就像您当初启发我一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in the way that you've inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有句成语能够用来形容我对您的钦佩\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I believe the French even have a word for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,法国人称之为\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when the men get together to honor their leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,五体投地\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They call it an homage, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-是五体投地  长官  -这全是屁话  麦考利\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-An homage, sir. -That's bullshit, McCawley!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但它是很中听的屁话\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it's very, very good bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:27.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,麦考利  你就像十五年前的我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}McCawley, you remind me of myself fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们现在讨论一下这个\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Which is why we need to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,坐下  年轻人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have a seat, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,英国人已经接受你加入雄鹰中队\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The British have accepted you into the Eagle Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你愿意\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're on your way to England tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,明天就可以动身\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}if you still want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,飞行员是英国能否打退希特勒的关键\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just a few British pilots are all that stand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也决定着欧洲战场的走向\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}between Hitler and total victory in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们非常需要援助\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're gonna need all the help they can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我马上出发  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir. Well, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,按照规定  我应该要求你再慎重考虑一下\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just for the record... I'm supposed to ask you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长官?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不管我们是否愿意\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sooner or later we're gonna be in this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,...美国参战只是时间问题\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}whether we like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们也需要优秀的飞行员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I'm gonna need all of my best pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:19.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所以我应该征询你是否愿意留下来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So it's my duty to ask you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,少校  你会怎么做?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Major, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果是我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不会吧  我开始谢顶了?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get out. Am I going bald right back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:38.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伙计  我是个帅小伙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Man, I am one good-looking son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可千万别死\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't you ever die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:44.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打仗你死不了  今晚你就要装一副快死的样子\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Die. That's exactly the concept you gotta work tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:48.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,往眼睛上抹点儿丁香油\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You put a drop of this clove oil under your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:51.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快忍不住的时候就去找护士\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and you let them sting and well up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,做个深呼吸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You get your nurse alone, take a breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:58.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后就热泪盈眶地对她说  宝贝\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}let her see your eyes listen and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们训练我去打仗\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Baby, they're training me for war...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我生死难测\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I don't know what'll happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果明天我一去不返\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but if I die tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:11.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我盼望今晚我俩能共度春宵\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}" I want to know that we lived all we could tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,来吧  伙计们  漂亮护士在等着咱们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, guys! We got nurses waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快点  再不走比利的头就要秃光了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, before the rest of his hair falls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这样的决定?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是杜立特点名派我去的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, Doolittle assigned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他希望我能够接受实战训练\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He wanted me to get some real... real combat training in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想什么呢?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那儿可没有训练  只有战争\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not training over there. It's war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,输家丢掉性命  赢家也一无所获\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where the losers die, and there aren't any winners...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,大家都身心疲惫  就像我老爸那样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}just guys who turn into broken-down wrecks... like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道  我能理解  丹尼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, I understand that, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但是我觉得我有责仁去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I feel like I got a duty to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,见鬼  别和我扯什么责任\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't preach to me about duty, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我和你一样都是军人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wear the same uniform you do.
