Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.41,0:35:36.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你怎么能知道哪有暗礁哪没有?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How do you know they're submerged if they're submerged?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.85,0:35:39.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,古斯  你到底在干什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Gooz, what in the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.39,0:35:41.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为他修冲浪板\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just trying to fix this surfboard thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.36,0:35:43.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,被礁石撞坏了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He keeps taking chunks off his nose on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.46,0:35:47.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,放假的时候还要继续搞我的新发明  古斯水平舵\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}On my day off, I'm working on my new invention, the Gooz Cruise Fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.51,0:35:52.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要发财啦! 所有的冲浪板都需要加装我的水平舵\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm gonna be a rich fella. Every surfboard in the nation's gonna need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.63,0:35:54.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你最好打扫干净\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah? Well, you're gonna need a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.97,0:35:56.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,瞧瞧新来的菜鸟\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Check out these new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.97,0:36:01.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嗨  啰哈\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hi. Aloha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.61,0:36:03.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们是飞行员吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You all pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:08.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好像很复杂  上面有不少开关和按钮\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're working on it. It's a lot of switches and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.22,0:36:13.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太平洋的骄傲\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Pride of the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.79,0:36:14.68,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们是谁?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.49,0:36:17.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,空中杀手\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Terrors of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.66,0:36:21.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,欢迎  小姐们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Welcome, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:27.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等我解决了这个黑屁股  再带你们逛逛\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have to deal with toasty sunburnt fanny before I can show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:38.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,亲爱的伊芙琳 一切都出乎我的意料\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ow! Dear Evelyn. It's different than I thought it would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:44.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿很冷、冷得刺骨\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's cold... so cold it goes deep into your bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.35,0:36:50.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但有一股暖流在我的胸中涌动  那就是我们的爱情\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There is one place I can go to find warmth. That is to think of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:52.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我祈祷能早日回到你的身旁\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just wish I could be back there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:36:57.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在这很难交到朋友\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not easy making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:01.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,两天前  一对皇家飞行员夫妇  还和我们一起喝啤酒\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Two days ago, I had a beer... with a couple of the RAF pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.86,0:37:04.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,昨天他们双双阵亡\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yesterday, both of them got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:21.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,亲爱的雷夫  我对你的思念难以叙说\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dear Rafe. I miss you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.72,0:37:25.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,千山万水将我们阻隔\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's so strange to be half a world away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.93,0:37:28.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我咬住他了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm right on his tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.63,0:37:36.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打下一架\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.14,0:37:40.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,黄昏  我注视着斜阳\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Every night I look at the sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.83,0:37:43.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,希望留住最后的余辉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and try to draw the last ounce of heat from its long day...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.71,0:37:47.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,用我的心温暖远方的爱人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and send it from my heart to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.35,0:37:54.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,家人吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.69,0:37:59.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,女友  长官  我的意中人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Girl, sir. The girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.83,0:38:05.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,许多人责怪美国人不参战\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A lot of people frown on the Yanks for not being in this war yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.90,0:38:10.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只想说  要是每个美国军人都跟你一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd just like to say... if there are many more back home like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.80,0:38:13.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谁都不敢与美国为敌\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}God help anyone who goes to war with America.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.85,0:38:22.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,礼仪分队  持枪!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Atten-hut! Attention on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.77,0:38:26.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太平洋舰队总司令金梅尔上将登舰\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral Kimmel... Commander-in-Chief, Pacific Fleet, on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.39,0:38:27.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,士气很高昂  上校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sharp presentation, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:29.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢  将军\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Admiral Kimmel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.62,0:38:31.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,已经四个月了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}For four months now Washington's been
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.12,0:38:33.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,华盛顿闭口不谈日本的威胁\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}blowing pink smoke about the threat from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.03,0:38:37.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这可能会影响我们的士气  我特别强调不能放松警惕\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Could make us lose our fighting edge. I'm determined not to let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.14,0:38:47.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,对不起  上校  将军  华盛顿急电\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}With your permission, Captain. Admiral, urgent, from Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.75,0:38:56.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太平洋舰队正在积极准备对抗日本人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm supposed to keep this fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.01,0:38:58.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,保卫覆盖半个地球的太平洋\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}battle-ready to take on the Japanese... cover half the damn globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.62,0:39:00.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在他们却要调十二艘驱逐舰到大西洋\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now they want me to transfer another
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.90,0:39:03.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们不知道我们也面临危险吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}twelve destroyers to the Atlantic. Don't they know what we're facing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.16,0:39:05.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们认为欧洲的战事是最紧要的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They feel Europe is the greater danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.39,0:39:08.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有人考虑夏威夷的危险吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm assuming these risk assessments include Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.36,0:39:11.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,珍珠港水浅  敌人不能实施鱼雷攻击\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Pearl Harbor is too shallow for an aerial torpedo attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.15,0:39:12.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而且受到潜艇的保护\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're surrounded by sub nets.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.97,0:39:14.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,唯一需要担心的是敌人破坏我们的飞机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All we need worry about is sabotage...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.10,0:39:18.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所以我们把飞机集中起来  方便保护\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so we bunched our planes together to make them easier to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.60,0:39:20.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,距离是天然的屏障  将军\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Distance is our ally, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.11,0:39:23.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们分析了所有的可能性  对吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You analysts got it all figured out, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.04,0:39:28.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,聪明的敌人常常会出其不意痛击你自以为很安全的地方\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The smart enemy hits you exactly where you think you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.03,0:39:51.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我从观光飞机上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.00,0:39:55.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,拍到军舰和空军基地的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.14,0:39:58.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这些军舰都停靠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.98,0:40:01.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是最明显的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.86,0:40:15.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为了适应水深我们改装了鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.50,0:40:21.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,加装了木鳍
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.07,0:40:25.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,鱼雷就可以在浅水中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.67,0:40:31.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,趁珍珠港还没有苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.28,0:40:33.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要发起猛烈的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.13,0:40:54.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我修理了液压和电器系统  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In coming! I fixed the hydraulics and electrics, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.47,0:40:56.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但是来不及修理油管\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but the oil hoses still need attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.30,0:40:57.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,启动引擎吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just crank it, lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.84,0:40:59.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,祝你好运  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}God speed you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.48,0:41:11.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,红队  攻击轰炸机  蓝队  盯住战斗机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Red section, take the bombers. Blue section, look out for the fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.65,0:41:16.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,轰炸机在前方  咱们给他们点颜色瞧瞧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bombers dead ahead. Let's dropin and give them a reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.43,0:41:23.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,红二号  跟着我  爬高  攻击领头的轰炸机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Red Two, follow my lead, high side. Go right at the lead bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.36,0:41:24.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好的  红一号\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Following you, Red One.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.31,0:41:33.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打得好\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good hit! Good hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.68,0:41:40.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,红一号  转回来攻击敌机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Red One, coming around, reset for the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.22,0:41:44.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我锁定中间那一架\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have the middle bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.86,0:41:49.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hammer down!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.33,0:41:57.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打中了  打得好  红二号\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We got him. Nice shot, Red Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.20,0:41:59.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,正前方有两架敌机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I got two M.E. s dead ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.97,0:42:07.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我盯着他  让我来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm on him. I'm on his tail.
