Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.93,0:48:07.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你知道吗  他教我飞行\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, he taught me to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.73,0:48:13.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,无论我遇到任何麻烦  我都不会束手无策\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I always knew that no matter what trouble I got into... I'd never be in it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.47,0:48:15.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他总会帮我渡过难关\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He'd be there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.88,0:48:21.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就是在天上他也逼着我超过别人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was always pushing me to be better and faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.32,0:48:26.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他说你是个了不起的飞行员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He told me you were a great flier.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.19,0:48:31.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那天晚上他告诉我  他自愿去英国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It was the same night he told me he'd volunteered to go to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.69,0:48:35.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,自愿?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Volunteered?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.43,0:48:41.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他跟我说他是被指派去的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He... he told me he'd been assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.37,0:48:47.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他总是在设法保护我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was always trying to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.31,0:48:56.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但是你知道吗?我看着镜子里面  穿着这身制服的自己\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you know what? I look at myself in the mirror in this uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.25,0:48:58.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我都不知道我是谁\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I still don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.89,0:49:04.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我看起来像英雄吗?我感觉不是\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I look like a hero... but I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.19,0:49:14.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫  他一向都是表里如一  不是吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe... he always looked the part, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.10,0:49:17.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他无法等到成为英雄的那一天了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He couldn't wait to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.63,0:49:46.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,敬雷夫·麦考利  最棒的飞行员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To Rafe McCawley. The best pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.10,0:49:49.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我曾经最好的朋友\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and the best friend I ever knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.17,0:49:51.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我一生最好的朋友\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or ever will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.11,0:49:57.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,敬雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.98,0:50:06.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(为国捐躯)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.23,0:50:20.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,攻击训练正在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.63,0:50:22.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为保证任务成功
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.87,0:50:26.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,高空轰炸及鱼雷攻击训练是极为重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.74,0:50:27.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,只要偷袭顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.04,0:50:29.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美国人只有坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.01,0:50:37.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,制造大量的假情报麻痹美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.12,0:50:39.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,特别要关注太平洋的主要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.82,0:50:44.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,尤其是夏威夷  不能放松
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.42,0:50:46.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你太英明了  山本大将
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.99,0:50:53.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,英明的人能避免战争
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.40,0:50:58.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(一九四一年七月  华盛顿)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.14,0:51:02.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(海军司令部)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.37,0:51:04.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你看看\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.61,0:51:07.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太平洋上到处都是日本人的电报\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Japanese are flooding the Pacific with radio traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.88,0:51:10.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从巴拿马运河到东南亚都有\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everywhere from the Panama Canal to southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.45,0:51:12.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这不合乎逻辑  上校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's no logical pattern, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.18,0:51:13.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,对  这其中必有玄机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No. There's always logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.75,0:51:16.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们知道我们在监听\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They know we read their mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.49,0:51:20.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们想让我们以为他们的舰队在向南移动\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're trying to make us think their fleet is moving south.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.66,0:51:25.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不吃这一套  其中肯定有阴谋\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not buying it. Something, something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.80,0:51:29.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,否则  这也太明目张胆了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Otherwise, why would they take the trouble to bullshit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.02,0:51:47.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊芙琳  我替你签收了这些信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evelyn, I signed for these letters for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.82,0:51:51.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从英国寄来的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.16,0:51:52.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫的信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're from Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.76,0:51:57.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,很抱歉  伊芙琳  邮件比消息慢\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry, Evelyn. You know how long it takes mail to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.77,0:52:10.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(三个月后)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.54,0:52:14.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(正在上映  卓别林 - 大独裁者)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.95,0:52:17.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(新闻剪辑)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.22,0:52:20.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美国还在等待日本的和平答复\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}America still awaits Japan's response to peace proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.69,0:52:23.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,野村大使抵达首都华盛顿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ambassador Nomura arrives in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.35,0:52:27.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,希望他的到来能够达成太平洋地区的和平协议\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...in what could hopefully guarantee continued peace in the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.69,0:52:30.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,英国方面  邱吉尔宣称\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}On the British front, Churchill declares
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.11,0:52:32.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,只要美国支持我们就能获胜\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Give us the tools, and we will finish the job."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.45,0:52:38.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,皇家空军在英吉利海峡誓死捍卫英国领空\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The RAF has fought bravely against Hitler's ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.57,0:52:41.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,让希特勒的野心无法得逞\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...to rule the skies over the Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.01,0:52:46.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,胜利来之不易  许多优秀飞行员献出了生命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Victory does not come without sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.68,0:52:49.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊芙琳\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evelyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.98,0:52:53.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,丹尼  真巧啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Danny. Hey. Some comedy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.55,0:53:00.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-好久不见  -我一直在进行训练\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-It's been a while. -I've been logging a lot offlight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.32,0:53:03.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我也一直碰不到你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I kinda been avoiding you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.93,0:53:08.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想不想  你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look... Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.30,0:53:09.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.50,0:53:11.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sure, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.80,0:53:15.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我记得我七岁那年  有一次\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I remember this one time when I was like, seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.01,0:53:17.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那时候我老是爱做一些小玩艺儿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was always building gadgets and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.60,0:53:21.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫让我给他做一对翅膀  他就能像他老爸一样飞行\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He wanted me to build him some wings so he could fly like his daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.94,0:53:25.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我说没有引擎就飞不了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told him you can't fly without some kind of engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.15,0:53:29.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但是他不肯听  他说  我叫你做就做\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But he wouldn't listen. "Danny, never mind that, just build them anyway."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.28,0:53:32.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只好照办了  我爬到谷仓上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So I did. And I'm up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.35,0:53:34.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,帮他把大翅膀绑在身上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}strapping these big old wings on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.86,0:53:39.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是我们用偷来的废纸、胶水和破布黏起来的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...that we made from paper and glue and these massive silk bloomers that we stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.53,0:53:44.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他的样子好蠢  我说  你不能这样从谷仓上跳下去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He looked so stupid, and I told him "You can't jump off the barn in these."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.63,0:53:48.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后一声巨响  他摔断了一条腿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And bam! He busted his leg on a backhoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.07,0:53:55.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我好想念他\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}God, I miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.57,0:54:00.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想不到的是隔天他又爬上了屋顶\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But don't you think that Rafe wasn't back up there next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.25,0:54:05.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,包着石膏  还叫我把翅膀做一些调整\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cast and everything, telling me to make some adjustments on those wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.95,0:54:07.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们看\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.65,0:54:14.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,塔希提岛  太平洋的中心  一千七百英里!帅呆了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Crossroads of the Pacific. Tahiti - 1,700 miles! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.23,0:54:16.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,瞧   贝蒂\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Say, Betty...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.01,0:54:27.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不要  快起来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Betty! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.14,0:54:28.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,怎么回事?雷德\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's going on, Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.18,0:54:29.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你要站起来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stand up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.38,0:54:30.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What do you mean?
