Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.15,1:10:48.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是一个月前才建成的  还没有检测过\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Which is a month old, Admiral, and untested.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:51.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我也见过这些新雷达  少校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've seen these new radar screens, Major.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.88,1:10:53.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它们根本分辨不出\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's no way of telling whether they're ours,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.32,1:10:54.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是敌机还是该死的鸟\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}theirs or a flock of damn birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.19,1:10:57.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(一九四一年十二月五日  珍珠港)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.39,1:11:00.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我监听到一个来自东京打到珍珠港附近某地的电话\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm intercepting a call from Tokyo to somewhere close by Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.16,1:11:03.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,东京来的  他说不认识你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's a call from Tokyo. They say they don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.89,1:11:09.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你好?是我  喂  喂\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hello? Hai. Moshi, moshi
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.01,1:11:19.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是个当地牙医  他说从他的办公室可以看到珍珠港\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's a local dentist. He can see Pearl Harbor from his office.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.35,1:11:21.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,对方问有很多水手吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are there many sailors around?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:30.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,牙医说航空母舰没在港口\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uh, the dentist says that the flatships are not in port.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.02,1:11:33.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们在谈天气\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're talking about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.49,1:11:35.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他好像不知道对方是谁\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He doesn't seem to know who he's talking to.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.13,1:11:43.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,喂?你好  喂? 莫名其妙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hello? Moshi moshi. Hello? That was a strange call.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.14,1:11:48.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将军  能单独向您汇报吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral, may I speak to you in private?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.31,1:11:52.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,间谍为什么敢用电话? 他们知道我们在进行监听\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why would a spy use a phone? They know we tap all international lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:54.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,监听人员认为他们并没有使用暗语\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our listeners feel it's probably not code talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.78,1:11:57.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听起来好像日本人想从本地居民口中\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It sounds like someone in Japan is sneaking
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.32,1:11:59.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打探我们的航空母舰在哪\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}around asking a local citizen the location of our carriers.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.19,1:12:03.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这让我觉得心里很乱  马上通知联邦调查局\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, that makes me feel all warm inside. Get the FBI on it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.12,1:12:06.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们还没找到那该死的日本舰队吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have we found the goddamn Japanese Fleet yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.46,1:12:08.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,还没有  将军  我们正在整个太平洋上搜索\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Admiral. The bases are looking all over the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.93,1:12:11.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是不是该死的日本舰队在钻石海峡转悠\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So the entire fleet could be rounding Diamond Head
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.14,1:12:12.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所以我们才一无所知\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and we wouldn't know a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.07,1:12:14.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,继续寻找\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.02,1:12:50.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我还活着\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.09,1:12:53.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太困难了  我们没办法通知你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is the first I could get word out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.66,1:13:28.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(法语)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.45,1:13:55.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我答应过你一定会回来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told you I'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.02,1:14:05.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,来  坐吧  都过去了  没事了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here, sit down. Sit down. Come here. It's OK. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.73,1:14:09.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真的是你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're real.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.00,1:14:11.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.77,1:14:14.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我每天都梦想这一天\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wished for this every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.57,1:14:18.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我也是  我每分每秒都在想你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know. Me, too. Every second. So did I.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.24,1:14:22.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我以为你死了  他们说你被击落  掉进了海里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I thought you were dead. They said you were shot down in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.82,1:14:25.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.35,1:14:30.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我掉进海里  冷极了  我好想你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was in the ocean. It was so cold. I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.39,1:14:34.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,后来  法国渔船救起了我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I got picked up by a French fishing boat...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.29,1:14:37.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在法国的被占区  我不能写信给你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I was in occupied France, and I couldn't get word out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.26,1:14:39.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我差一点就  我会全部告诉你的  我保证\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I'm just... I'll tell you all about it, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.26,1:14:42.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在好啦  我回来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I'm fine. I'm OK. And I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.07,1:14:48.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊芙琳  我好想见到你  你太美啦\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evelyn... I just wanted to see you. You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.02,1:15:06.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.10,1:15:14.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嘿  都过去了  伊芙琳  我回来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, it's OK. It's OK. Evelyn, Evelyn. I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.40,1:15:19.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没事了  我发誓永远也不离开你了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's OK. I won't leave you again, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.94,1:15:22.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫  你死了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe, you died.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.68,1:15:26.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的心也死了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And so did I.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.85,1:15:30.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道  我现在回来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know, but I'm... I'm... It's fine now. I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.12,1:15:33.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们团聚了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're together.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.49,1:15:43.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们又团聚了  对吧?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I mean, we are together... right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.00,1:15:48.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不知道我在哪\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.94,1:15:53.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.04,1:16:23.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.94,1:16:29.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,离我远点\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.18,1:16:34.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.78,1:16:38.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这里是檀香山电台\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is Radio Honolulu...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.36,1:16:40.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在这个令人愉快的太平洋岛屿上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}playing the sweetest music on the sweetest island
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.27,1:16:42.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在这个阳光明媚的十二月六日\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.32,1:16:45.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们为你送上优美的音乐\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's a beautiful December 6th with beautiful music
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.76,1:16:48.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要是美国人起了疑心
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.66,1:16:50.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们的广播会告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.54,1:17:00.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.57,1:17:02.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,噢  我的妈呀\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.27,1:17:04.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真正的王牌飞行员!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There you go. A real live ace!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.35,1:17:08.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,王牌飞行员才击落了五架敌机  而我击落了六架\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whoo! An ace is only five. I shot down six M.E.s.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.51,1:17:10.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,还有两架打冒了烟  他们没算进去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I got two smokers, too. They don't count them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.95,1:17:13.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我还没有受勋  就被打下来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Of course, I got shot down myself before they could pin me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.25,1:17:14.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那你从前线回来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So you got back from behind enemy lines, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.73,1:17:16.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打仗到底是什么感觉?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's that combat like?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.06,1:17:18.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你害怕吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.72,1:17:20.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嗨!一个一个来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! One at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.83,1:17:23.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,纳粹空军的技术非常棒\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, them Luftwaffe boys can fly pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.23,1:17:25.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你要知道  这跟训练可是两码事儿  他们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not like, you know, training. They're, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.47,1:17:33.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,丹尼  知道吗  他们很讲究战术\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Danny. You know, they're all about tactics is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.57,1:17:35.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,纳粹飞行员比你飞得快\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}See, the Nazis, right, they're faster than you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.60,1:17:37.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们钻进云层  一个俯冲\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so they'll disappear and they get up in
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.75,1:17:39.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就到你头顶\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the soup and they'll throw like a roll or a hammerhead...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.01,1:17:42.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后像某些美国人一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and they'll come around on your high side
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.01,1:17:44.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从背后偷袭你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}shoot you from behind like some Americans will.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.12,1:17:53.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,古斯  这才是真正的王牌\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey... Gooz, you're looking at a real live ace.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.96,1:17:57.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,让我把这件衬衫脱下来送给你!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, let me give you the shirt off my back!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.96,1:17:59.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,拿去吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.77,1:18:01.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll take it from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.90,1:18:02.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,反正我也需要便服\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can see how you all been spending your time out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.76,1:18:04.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嘿  雷夫  我们得谈谈  好吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, Rafe, we gotta talk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.80,1:18:07.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我和你没什么好谈的  过来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I got nothing to talk about with you. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.57,1:18:10.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,干一杯吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why don't you have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.31,1:18:13.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我来敬酒\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.65,1:18:16.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为了死里逃生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To returning from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.78,1:18:19.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真没想到  可这就是生活\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wasn't all I expected, but, well, that's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.22,1:18:23.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,敬我最好的朋友  丹尼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To my best friend and loyal buddy Danny...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.86,1:18:26.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为了他所做的一切干杯\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for keeping up the war effort back here at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.23,1:18:35.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,知道吗  在英国有人向你敬酒你却不喝\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, where I come from somebody makes a toast to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.89,1:18:37.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那就是不给别人面子\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...and you don't drink that's saying something.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.84,1:18:41.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧  雷夫  既然话都说到这个份上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All right, Rafe. That's how it's gonna be
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.91,1:18:43.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为你干杯!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.91,1:18:46.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我想  你们两个需要单独谈谈\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, you guys need to spend some time alone, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.21,1:18:47.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不  别走  雷德\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Aw, hell, no, Red. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.31,1:18:50.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不  不  我们就在这儿庆祝\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, no, no. We're celebrating here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.85,1:18:55.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在前方打仗  差点送了命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Me over there fighting... almost getting killed...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.12,1:18:58.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的朋友丹尼在后方  照顾我的一切\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}my friend Danny back here... looking after my interests for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.89,1:19:00.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你知道吗  他太好了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You all know Danny was even good enough
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.38,1:19:02.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好得连我的女朋友都给照顾了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to look out for my girl for me while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.73,1:19:05.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们以为你阵亡了  雷夫  我们都很悲痛\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We thought you were dead, Rafe. And it gutted us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.30,1:19:08.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可我们总还要继续生活下去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And we were just trying to get on with our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.60,1:19:09.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你过得不错  对吧?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Life is good, ain't it, Danny?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.30,1:19:12.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你这个烂酒鬼  不讲道理  一直都是这样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, you're a rotten drunk. You always have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.47,1:19:16.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你这个卑鄙的朋友  我才发现\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, you're a lousy friend. That's a new development.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.54,1:19:19.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你扔下她为别人去打仗\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You left her to fight somebody else's war...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.05,1:19:21.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你还设法不让我去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and you made damn sure that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.43,1:19:22.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们真的以为你死啦!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't go with you and we thought that you were dead
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.91,1:19:25.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是差点就死了  你这个狗娘养的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I almost did die, you little son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.07,1:19:27.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那时候我想到的只有她\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And her face was the last thing that went through my mind...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.62,1:19:29.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别站在那告诉我这一切都是理所当然的!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so don't stand there and tell me to act like it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.96,1:19:31.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不错  雷夫  我是留下了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, Rafe, well, I stayed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.56,1:19:34.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你得知道情况改变了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I stayed, and you made sure of that and
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.82,1:19:37.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我希望你能接受现实\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}some things changed. And I hope you can get used to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.20,1:19:42.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,噢  我要接受现实? 好  让你看看我怎样接受的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, I have to get used to it? All right. We'll see how I can get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.07,1:19:47.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,接受我的拳头吧  小子!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get used to that, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.34,1:19:48.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只用左手就够了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, hey! And that's my left hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.31,1:19:58.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有人在打架  快派宪兵来!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Melee at the Hula-la. Send M.P. s!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.02,1:20:03.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你说我是卑鄙的朋友?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You called me a lousy friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.06,1:20:11.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可恶  来啊  丹尼!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ow! Shit! Come on, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.30,1:20:21.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-逮捕他们! -快跑啊!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Let's go get them. -Let's move out!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.78,1:20:27.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们会被关禁闭的  快走!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're gonna throw us in the brig. Let's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.59,1:20:46.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,编队在珍珠港北三百二十海里处待命
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.25,1:21:06.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,帝国的兴衰在此一役！
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.36,1:21:20.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫  你是我唯一的亲人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rafe... you're the only family I got.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.03,1:21:25.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你不在的时候  我孤独极了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When you were gone it was the loneliest I'd ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.62,1:21:27.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她和我一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The same for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.67,1:21:30.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,噢  小子  你现在真的是让我心都碎了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, boy, now you're really breaking my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.68,1:21:32.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你要是没走  什么都不会发生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you hadn't gone, none of this woulda happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.74,1:21:34.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这么说我猜是我错了?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, so it's my fault, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.98,1:21:36.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,算了吧  雷夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Damn it, Rafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.52,1:21:44.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我看我们总会有办法\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just know there's got to be some way...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.05,1:21:50.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,妥善解决这个问题  让我们和好如初\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we can work things out so that... things could be right between me and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.62,1:21:54.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我看永远也不可能了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just don't see how it could ever be the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.40,1:22:03.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,尊敬的父亲\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Revered father...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.77,1:22:10.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在我要去执行任务  完成我的使命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I go now to full-fill my mission and my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.61,1:22:16.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我希望能为我们全家带来荣誉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I hope it is a destiny that will bring honor to our family...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.61,1:22:19.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果需要付出生命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and if it reguires my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.52,1:22:23.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我将在所不辞  精忠报国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I will sacrifice it gladly to be a good servant of our nation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.80,1:23:47.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嘿  我看到一大片阴影\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey... we got a large haze.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.67,1:23:52.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,太大了不象飞机  对吧?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's too big to be planes, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.15,1:23:59.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想走这步? 要跳马?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is that what you wanna do? Knight to knight five?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.62,1:24:01.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,臭棋!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wrong move.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.58,1:24:04.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长官! 雷达显示东北部有大量回波\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lieutenant, radar's picking up a large return moving in from the northeast.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.89,1:24:05.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.49,1:24:08.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.82,1:24:11.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是从本土回来的 B-17 轰炸机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's a flight of B-17s coming in from the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.13,1:24:14.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没什么可担心的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.76,1:24:16.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是一大群 B-17 轰炸机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A heck of a lot of B-17s.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.10,1:24:20.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,打得好\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good shot, Hop.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.67,1:24:25.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这次有好点的消息了吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This better be good, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.94,1:24:29.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的驱逐舰击沉了一艘日本潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One of our destroyers reports having fired and sunk...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.22,1:24:33.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,该潜艇于六时五十三分企图闯入珍珠港\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}enemy submarine attempting to enter Pearl Harbor at 0653.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.68,1:24:34.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在七时二十分了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's 7:20!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.68,1:24:35.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,译电耽误了  将军\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We had decoder delays, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.92,1:24:37.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,马上报告华盛顿  立即召集全部参谋人员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Relay this to Washington. Recall the staff.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.96,1:24:47.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,和谈  失败  "终止谈判"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Failure..."Peace talks..."useless."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.36,1:24:50.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是瑟曼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thurman here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.57,1:24:52.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,东京指示驻华盛顿使馆\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tokyo transmitting to their embassy in Washington
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.76,1:24:55.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"立即破坏译码机"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Discontinue use of your decoding machine...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.18,1:24:57.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"销毁秘密文件"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"and dispose of immediately. "Special emphasis on destroying important parts."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.58,1:24:59.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你看到了吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you read that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.98,1:25:10.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将军  海军情报局截获了东京\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral... Naval Intel intercepted a transmission from Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.55,1:25:12.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,发给华盛顿日本使馆的电报\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...to the Japanese embassy in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.32,1:25:14.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,指示他们拆毁译码机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...instructing them to break apart all decoder machines
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.64,1:25:17.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,烧掉全部秘密文件\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and burn all secret documents.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.33,1:25:19.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本人要开战了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Japanese are expecting a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.80,1:25:21.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们是不是也该\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Should we?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.52,1:25:49.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可以进行偷袭了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.98,1:26:12.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,警惕日本人可能从任何方向发起的进攻\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Warning of possible Japanese aggressive movement in any direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.98,1:26:15.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"中断关系  开始战争"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Broken relationship. Hostilities imminent."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.05,1:26:17.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,战争会在哪儿开始?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But where?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.02,1:26:58.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你曾经打输过吗  米勒?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did you ever lose a fight, Miller?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.89,1:27:01.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,很走运  还没有  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I been lucky so far, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.70,1:27:04.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,据我所知  这不仅仅是运气\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From what I hear, it ain't luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.00,1:27:07.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你是我们军舰的骄傲\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ship's proud of you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.10,1:27:46.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,星期天海军这么早就搞飞行训练吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why the hell's the Navy doing practice this early on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.95,1:28:28.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.87,1:28:51.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快走  快走\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get down! Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.44,1:28:56.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是海军新闻记者  我可以确定  海军没这种飞机!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm with Navy news reel, and I can tell you one thing... them ain't Navy planes!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.25,1:29:04.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们遭到轰炸! 我们遭到轰炸! 快起来! 快起来!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're being bombed! We're being bombed! Get up! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.53,1:29:19.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.27,1:29:21.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(亚利桑纳号)
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.54,1:29:29.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所有人员进入战斗位置\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Man your battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.51,1:29:31.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,又是演习\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Another dumb drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.53,1:29:50.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼东西?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.80,1:29:51.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是炸弹!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.67,1:29:53.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快走  快走  快走!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.11,1:30:01.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,狗日的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Son of a bi...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.42,1:30:11.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,给我接轮机舱\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get me the engine room!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.09,1:30:16.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.36,1:30:25.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,汇报战斗状况! 所有人员进入战斗位置!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Report battle stations! Manned and ready! Man your battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.67,1:30:28.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是来真的! 亚利桑纳被击沉了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is no shit! They just sunk the Arizona!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.87,1:30:30.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,全面警戒!全面警戒!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Generalguarters! Generalguarters!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.93,1:30:34.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所有人员进入战斗位置!这不是演习!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All hands, man your battle stations! This is no damn drill!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.54,1:30:38.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快!快!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.48,1:30:42.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好像是日本飞机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They look like Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.42,1:30:44.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不明白日本人为什么会恨我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't even know the Japs were sore at us!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.85,1:30:46.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,丹尼  我他妈要有架飞机就好了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Danny, you just get me to a goddamn airplane!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.99,1:30:53.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的老天爷! 好精采的片段  看到了吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Holy God! This is good footage. Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.63,1:30:55.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的妈呀\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.46,1:30:57.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,希望机场还没被炸掉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I hope there's still an airfield left.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.22,1:31:54.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,大家快赶去医院\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everybody to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.61,1:32:09.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,海军的飞机在干什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why's the Navy always buzzing us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.21,1:32:12.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷德  闭嘴!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Shut up, Red!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.05,1:32:17.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷德  现在还早啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Red, it's too early.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.58,1:32:19.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本鬼子来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Japs are here!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.59,1:32:23.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么鬼玩意儿?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.99,1:32:25.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快跑!快跑!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.39,1:33:00.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,叫医务员上舰桥来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get corpsmen to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.39,1:33:01.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.90,1:33:11.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  第三甲板左侧被淹没了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Repair says third deck is flooding portside!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.69,1:33:35.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,起来  胆小鬼!快去战斗!快去!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get up! Get up, you cowards! Get up there and fight! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.17,1:33:50.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我来了  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I got you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.44,1:33:52.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,用无线电请求空中支援!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You radio for air cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.64,1:33:54.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开始伤患抑制!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Initiate damage control!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.58,1:33:58.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,找到我的 X.O.  叫副舰长负责指挥  确保炮手\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Find my X.O. Tell him to assume command. And you make sure the gunners...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.75,1:34:04.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  所有人都已就位  你把我们训练得很好\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everyone's where they need to be, Captain. You trained us well. You trained us well.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.06,1:34:08.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.56,1:34:43.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,走  快走!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go, go, go, go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.99,1:34:46.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快走!大家快逃啊!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go! Everybody move!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.10,1:34:52.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去拿机枪子弹!去拿子弹!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get the ammo for that fifty cal! Get that fifty cal!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.51,1:35:00.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go!
