Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.72,2:01:04.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别让他们进来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Keep them outside!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.16,2:01:09.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在这儿等\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.40,2:01:12.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别碰我   日本鬼子  把你的臭手拿开\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't touch me, you Jap! Get your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.07,2:01:16.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,带到加护病房\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get him into critical. Get him off me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.30,2:01:17.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,加护病房  向前走!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Critical, frontward!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.78,2:01:21.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我伤得多重?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How bad am I?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.78,2:01:23.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你不会有事\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're gonna be just fine, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.81,2:01:25.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不想死\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't wanna die.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.38,2:01:27.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你不会死的  我会帮你的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're not gonna die. I've got your hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.05,2:01:31.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有足够的吗啡给他止疼吗? 他快不行了  给他注射吗啡\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you have enough morphine to make him comfortable? He won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.45,2:01:34.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,让重伤患排好队!给他吗啡  把他们带过去!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Line the critical up! Get him morphine. Take him over there!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.82,2:01:36.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,把烧伤病人带到树下\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Burn victims by the tree!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.42,2:01:40.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我刚发现她  好像已经死了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just found her! I don't think she's breathing.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.63,2:01:43.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她死了  把她\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, she's dead. Take her...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.13,2:01:47.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,噢  天啊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.24,2:01:53.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你确定吗?再检查一次  -她已经死了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Are you sure, Ev? Check her again. -She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.78,2:01:54.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,抱她过去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take her over there!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.64,2:01:57.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你一定要确定清楚\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you've gotta be sure!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.48,2:01:59.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她死了  快回去工作  桑得拉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She's dead! Go back to work, Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.68,2:02:02.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不知道该做什么\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.68,2:03:39.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上将  华盛顿的电报\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral? From Washington.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.52,2:03:44.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,[日本人的攻击迫在眉睫]\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Attack by Japan considered imminent."
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.52,2:03:50.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们只晚了一个小时\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're only an hour late.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.63,2:04:25.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.56,2:04:32.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只怕这样做会唤醒了在沉睡中的巨人
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.22,2:04:49.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们能做点儿什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How can we help?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.58,2:04:51.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们需要血  来吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We need blood. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.12,2:04:59.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,孩子  你要保持信仰  记住耶稣基督的话\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Remember, son, hold on to your faith.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.76,2:05:02.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今日你将随我进天堂\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Today you will be with me in paradise...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.50,2:05:05.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不要恐惧  我的孩子\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"so fear not." Fear not, my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.70,2:05:10.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你受到祝福  将蒙主荣召\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You are a man truly blessed. You will die in a state of grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.01,2:05:14.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,痛苦很短暂、荣耀是永恒的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Remember, pain is temporary, but glory is forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.88,2:05:20.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,坚信主耶稣基督  很快便将与上帝与天使同在\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hold on to your faith, my son. You'll be with God, the saints, and the angels soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.58,2:05:28.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我赦免你犯下的过错  以圣父、圣子、圣灵之名\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I absolve you of your sins... in the name of the Father, the Son, the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.76,2:05:30.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In nomine patris et fili, et spiritus sancti. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.93,2:05:38.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,与上帝同在\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go with God, my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.61,2:05:47.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的人都困在码头\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've got men trapped everywhere in the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.04,2:05:49.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有力气搬得动东西的快来帮忙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We need help from anybody who can move.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.42,2:05:57.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,救我们出去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's somebody in here!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.75,2:06:02.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿有人  快派人下去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get somebody down here! They're cutting through!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.77,2:06:13.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿也有人  快派人下去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I hear somebody! Get some guys uphere!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.04,2:06:15.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,用力拉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Pull!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.57,2:06:21.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快救我们出去!水快满了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get us out! It's filling with water!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.62,2:06:23.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快拿输气管过来!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get an airline in here!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.98,2:06:28.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们该怎么做?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.52,2:06:35.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,速度不能再快了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It won't cut any faster!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.59,2:06:39.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快把它钊开\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cut him out! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.20,2:07:19.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,昨天  一九四一年十二月七日\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yesterday... December 7, 1941...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.44,2:07:24.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将永远成为我们的国耻日\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a date which will live in infamy...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.87,2:07:30.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美利坚合众国遭到日本\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the United States of America was suddenly and deliberately attacked...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.77,2:07:35.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,海空军有预谋的突然袭击\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}by naval and air forces of the Empire of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.65,2:07:43.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,显然易见  这次袭击是经过长期精心策划的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is obvious that planning the attack began many weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.16,2:07:48.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在此期间  日本政府\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}During the intervening time... the Japanese government...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.25,2:07:53.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,通过虚伪的声明和维护和平的宣传\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}has deliberately sought to deceive the United States by false statements...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.35,2:07:58.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,蓄意欺骗美国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and expressions of hope for continued peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.31,2:08:03.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,昨天对夏威夷群岛的攻击\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The attack yesterday on the Hawaiian Islands...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.28,2:08:09.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,使美国军队遭受重创\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}has caused severe damage to American military forces.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.45,2:08:16.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我沉痛地告诉各位  有三千多美国人丧失了生命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I regret to tell you... that over 3,000 American lives have been lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.32,2:08:23.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,无论需要多长时间也要战胜  敌人预谋的侵略\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No matter how long it may take us... to overcome this premeditated invasion...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.40,2:08:30.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,正义的美国人民  必将赢得彻底的胜利\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the American people, in their righteous might... will win through to absolute victory.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.28,2:08:40.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,由于日本无故发动的卑鄙袭击\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because of this unprovoked, dastardly attack by Japan...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:40.38,2:08:44.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要求国会宣布进入战争状态\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I ask that the Congress declare a state of war.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.95,2:08:55.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是不是还有士兵被困在亚里桑那号里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is it true... men are still trapped alive inside the Arizona?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.53,2:08:59.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰内传来敲打声\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We can heartapping from inside the hull.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.77,2:09:02.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们正在尽力抢救  但他们被困在四十尺海底\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're doing everything we can to get to them... but they're forty feet below water.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.71,2:09:12.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美国人自以为所向无敌\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've been trained to think that we're invincible.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.15,2:09:16.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可我们最值得骄傲的战舰\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And now our proudest ships have been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.25,2:09:20.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,却被我们藐视的敌人击沉了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}by an enemy we considered inferior.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.25,2:09:26.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们被逼得无路可退  所以一定要马上反击\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're on the ropes, gentlemen. That's exactly why we have to strike back now.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.53,2:09:29.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们准备攻击马绍尔和吉尔伯特群岛\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll attack the Marshall and Gilbert Islands, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.46,2:09:33.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的意思是要攻击日本的心脏  就象他们攻击我们一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I mean hitting the heart of Japan the way they have hit us.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.17,2:09:40.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,总统先生  珍珠港遭袭击是缺乏准备造成的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. President... Pearl Harbor caught us unawares because we didn't face facts.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.98,2:09:43.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不过我们应该面对现实\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This isn't a time for ignoring them again.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.71,2:09:47.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们有远程轰炸机  但在日本附近没有基地\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We have long-range bombers, but no place to launch them.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.62,2:09:52.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,中途岛离日本太远  苏联也不会帮助我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Midway is too far, and Russia won't allow us... to launch a raid from there.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.95,2:09:54.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,海军上将?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.19,2:09:58.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,海军航空兵都是轻型飞机  载弹量低、航程短\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Navy's planes are small. They carry light loads and have a short range.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.01,2:10:01.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,只能够从距离日本几百英里的地方起飞才能够进行轰炸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'd have to get them within a few hundred miles of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.20,2:10:04.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这样的话  就必须动用航母  但是  如果我们失去航母\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'd risk our carriers, and if we lose our carriers...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.85,2:10:06.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们将丧失抵御入侵的能力\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...we'll have no shield against invasion.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.67,2:10:10.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有人见过不流血的胜利吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Does anyone in this room think victory is possible without facing danger?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.07,2:10:14.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要进行战争  就必然有危险\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We are at war. Of course there's a risk.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.44,2:10:18.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我们不能无视危险  总统先生  如果日本人继续进攻\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But consider the risk, Mr. President. If the Japanese invade us right now...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.05,2:10:22.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在我们能够挡住他们之前  他们可以打到芝加哥\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}they would reach Chicago before we could stop them.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.72,2:10:26.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.56,2:10:33.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在我双腿残疾之前  你们大多数人还不认识我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}most of you did not know me when I had the use of my legs.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.56,2:10:37.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那时  我强壮  充满自信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was strong and proud... and arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.93,2:10:44.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在我时时刻刻在问自己  为什么上帝让我做在轮椅上?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now I wonder, every hour of my life... why God put me into this chair.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.61,2:10:48.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,国民流露出失败的情绪\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But when I see defeat in the eyes of my countrymen...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.56,2:10:50.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而你们也是如此\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in your eyes, right now...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.88,2:10:53.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我开始认为上帝\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I start to think that maybe he brought me down...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.19,2:10:54.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就是让我来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for times like these...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.85,2:10:57.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,提醒大家我们到底是谁\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when we all need to be reminded who we truly are...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.27,2:11:00.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们永不放弃  决不低头!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that we will not give up or give in.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.02,2:11:03.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,尊敬的总统先生  恕我直言\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. President, with all respect, sir...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.07,2:11:04.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,您的要求是不可能办到的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}what you're asking can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.98,2:11:21.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.01,2:11:24.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别扶我  乔治  别扶我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get back, George! Get back.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.86,2:11:41.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别再告诉我  没有什么是不可能!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do not tell me... it can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.33,2:11:50.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本继续在南太平洋炫耀武力\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Japan continues its military conguest... throughout the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.81,2:11:55.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在国内  美国的自愿者在加紧工作\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But, backhome... millions of American workers band together...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.72,2:11:58.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为雪十二月七日之耻 努力生产武器\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}bringing factories to life to avenge Pearl Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.38,2:12:06.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,总统先生  我们制定了轰炸东京的计划\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. President, we have an idea how to bomb the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.29,2:12:10.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,很危险  但很大胆\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sir, it's risky... but it's bold.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.26,2:12:13.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你是谁?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.43,2:12:14.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I, sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.66,2:12:16.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是洛上校  总统先生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain Low, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.63,2:12:20.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是他拟制的计划  它是潜艇舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's a submariner. He came up with this idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.17,2:12:22.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我喜欢潜艇舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I like sub commanders.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.60,2:12:26.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们没时间讲废话  我也一样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They don't have time for bullshit, and neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.54,2:12:28.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开始吧  先生们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fire away, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.63,2:12:46.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上帝啊!你在哪里?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And where is God in all this?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.50,2:12:53.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的敌人认为神风在保护他们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our enemies believe a divine wind protects them.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:53.50,2:12:56.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可我们的朋友却在此长眠\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But we see our friends laid out there before us.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.92,2:13:17.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(西维吉尼亚号舰长)
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.29,2:13:20.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别了  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.82,2:13:46.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷夫·麦考利中尉、丹尼·沃克中尉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lieutenants Rafe McCawley, Daniel Walker.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.22,2:13:47.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  少校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, Major?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.99,2:13:50.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,两小时后  你们回本土\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're both going stateside. Fly out in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.89,2:13:51.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么事儿?长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What for, sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.16,2:13:53.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去问杜立特上校\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ask Colonel Doolittle.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.95,2:13:57.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.35,2:14:15.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们要出发\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're packing.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.92,2:14:20.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是任务\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Orders.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.19,2:14:22.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么样的任务?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What kind of orders?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.26,2:14:25.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,最高机密\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The top-secret kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.86,2:14:28.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也是最危险的?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The dangerous kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.60,2:14:32.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没看见丹尼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can't find Danny.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.67,2:14:33.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是你来这来的原因?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is that why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.90,2:14:36.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,来找丹尼?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Looking for Danny?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.40,2:14:38.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可能在和他的队友告别\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Probably saying good-bye to his squadron.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.91,2:14:40.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们现在归杜立特指挥\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've been assigned to Doolittle.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.35,2:14:51.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不是来找丹尼的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wasn't looking for Danny.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.79,2:15:00.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有一件事儿  在你走之前我想你应该知道\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I couldn't have you go away without you understanding something.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.67,2:15:07.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是吗  你什么都不必解释\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah. You don't have to explain anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.44,2:15:11.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要  因为你以为我没有爱过你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I do, because you're acting like I didn't love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.84,2:15:15.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊芙琳  爱你使我活了下来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evelyn, loving you kept me alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.79,2:15:28.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不然  在英国我早就死了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I should've died over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.16,2:15:32.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,当我掉进海里的时候  我向上帝承诺\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I was in that water, I made a deal with God.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:34.29,2:15:36.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我说我后悔极了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told him I was sorry...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.36,2:15:39.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为了当英雄  我离开了你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told him that I knew I'd been a fool for leaving you
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.56,2:15:41.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真是太傻了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}trying to go over there and be a hero...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.27,2:15:44.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我向上帝承诺  从今后我别无所求\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I promised I'd never ask for anything again...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.87,2:15:48.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,只要我能够再见你一面\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}...if I could just see you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:52.35,2:15:54.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你知道吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.82,2:15:56.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我觉得我值得这样做\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.02,2:16:02.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊芙琳  是你让我活了下来  是你把我带回了家\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You kept me alive, Evelyn. You brought me home.
