Dialogue: 0,2:25:31.14,2:25:32.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,两位\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fellas?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.31,2:25:33.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sir.
