Dialogue: 0,2:25:55.50,2:25:57.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长官  我们只有十六架轰炸机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, sir, we only have sixteen planes.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:58.13,2:25:59.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那又怎样?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So?
