Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.24,2:26:04.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,力量对比太悬殊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How much difference can we make?
