Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.92,2:26:21.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这次空袭  即使成功\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This raid, even if we make it through...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.25,2:26:24.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也微不足道\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}it'll only be a pinprick...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.39,2:26:26.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我们这是在直接打击他们的心脏\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but it'll be straight through their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.59,2:26:30.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,胜利属于那些信念坚定\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Victory belongs to those that believe in it the most...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:30.84,2:26:32.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,永不动摇的人们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and believe in it the longest.
