Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.11,2:26:46.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes?
