Dialogue: 0,2:26:49.28,2:26:53.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,当然记得 我还没感谢你呢\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, sure I do. I'm sorry. I've been meaning to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.29,2:26:54.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你的机会来了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, maybe you can.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:55.09,2:26:57.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我想去指挥所听听\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When the news comes in about the Doolittle boys
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.19,2:26:59.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,杜立特部下发回的消息\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I want to be in the command post.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.89,2:27:03.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不知道你在说什么\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry. I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:05.70,2:27:07.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这项任务?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How the hell do you know about this mission?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:09.24,2:27:11.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,算是不慎泄漏吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's call it an inadvertent disclosure.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:11.17,2:27:13.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是某个和你约会的飞行员说的?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Some flyboy you're dating shot his mouth off.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.01,2:27:17.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,实际上  是两名飞行员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Actually, it's about two pilots.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:17.62,2:27:20.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道他们面对巨大的危险\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know they're going into great danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:20.15,2:27:22.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只想在那儿亲耳听到\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just want to be there
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.02,2:27:23.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们生还或是牺牲的消息\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when the news tells us if they've lived or died.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:28.02,2:27:30.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要是其他军官早就把你扔进监狱了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Most officers would have thrown you in the brig.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.49,2:27:32.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要是别的护士早就顾不上你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Most nurses wouldn't keep their fingers plugged
Dialogue: 0,2:27:32.29,2:27:34.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没时间用手按住你流血的动脉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in your artery.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.37,2:27:42.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不能保证什么\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can't promise you anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:48.74,2:27:50.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,嘿  雷德\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, Red,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:50.11,2:27:54.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你以为他们选中我们是因为我们年轻  好说话吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you think they pickedus to do this bcause we're young and dumb?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:56.08,2:27:58.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,拜托  古斯  因为我们是精英\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, Gooz, we're the tip of the sword.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:02.72,2:28:05.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,(为了贝蒂)
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.87,2:28:19.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为了我们的日本之行  我搞到一些胜利雪茄\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In honor of our trip to Japan... I got us some victory cigars!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:21.51,2:28:24.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,拿去吧  放在靠近心脏的步袋里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There you go. Put that in your inside pocket, next to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:25.11,2:28:27.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,知道吗  杰克  这一仗可能会失败\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, Jack, we may lose this battle...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.61,2:28:29.68,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我们一定能赢得这场战争\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but we're gonna win this war.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.78,2:28:30.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你明白我的意思吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know how I know?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:31.08,2:28:32.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.15,2:28:37.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们  因为他们的杰出贡献\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Them. bcause they're rare.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:39.25,2:28:44.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为他们在这种关键时刻  自愿挺身而出\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And at times like these, you see them... stepping forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.60,2:28:50.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,自愿者的意志无坚不摧  杰克\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's nothing stronger than the heart of a volunteer, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.07,2:28:59.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在作战部的朋友不想让我指挥这次空袭\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My friends in the war department don't want me to lead this raid...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.15,2:29:01.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们说我太宝贵了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because they say I'm too valuable.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.38,2:29:04.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们不希望我跟我挑选的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They don't want me up in the air flying with the men
Dialogue: 0,2:29:04.60,2:29:06.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,飞行员一起出任务\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that I've chosen...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:06.32,2:29:09.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可他们是我挑选的  是我训练和逼出来的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that I've chewed out, cussed out, pushed to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.66,2:29:14.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我很尊重这些飞行员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and that I've come to respect.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:17.25,2:29:19.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们想让我在甲板上发号施令\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They want me to stand on the flightdeck and wave you off.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:19.93,2:29:21.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我不想那样做\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, I don't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.74,2:29:24.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要跟你们一起去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:29.54,2:29:33.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们明天下午起飞  轰炸完毕后去中国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We take off tomorrow afternoon... drop our fire, and head for China.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.48,2:29:38.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的任务是轰炸他们的军事目标  飞机工厂和坦克工厂\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our mission is to hit military targets... aircraft and tank factories.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.69,2:29:41.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上校  你说我们有返航引导信号\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Colonel, you've given us homing beacons...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.82,2:29:44.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但你又说  中国到处是日本军队\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but you said China is overrun with Japanese troops.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.69,2:29:46.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果信号中断  怎么办?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What if the beacons are switched off?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.73,2:29:49.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那就紧急迫降并尽量避免被日本人抓住\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bring her down any way you can...and do your best to avoid capture.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:49.76,2:29:52.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果必须在日本人的上空跳伞  我们该怎么办?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What if we have to bail out over Japan?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:53.03,2:29:57.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这种情况  我无可奉告\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, in that situation, I can't tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:57.63,2:29:58.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你会怎么做  上校?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What would you do, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:02.10,2:30:04.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我天生不会做俘虏\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wasn't built to be a prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.11,2:30:08.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所以我会先让机组跳伞\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so I would have my crew bail out.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:09.51,2:30:12.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后选择一个重要的军事目标驾机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd find the sweetest military target
Dialogue: 0,2:30:12.71,2:30:14.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,与敌人同归于尽\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I could and drive my plane right smack into the middle of it
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.04,2:30:20.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但这仅限于我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.85,2:30:26.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是四十五岁的老家伙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm forty-five years old. I'm an old man.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:26.09,2:30:29.01,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而你们还有很长的路要走\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You guys have your whole lives ahead of you...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.12,2:30:31.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一切由你们自己决定\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so what you do is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.53,2:30:40.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,再有几个小时就要开始行动了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The mission will launch in a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.23,2:30:41.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一九四二年四月十八日
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.77,2:30:43.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你就待在这\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You'll stay right in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:46.88,2:30:47.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这  待在这儿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:47.61,2:30:50.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别和她们说话  她们也没空理你的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't talk to them. They won't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.74,2:30:53.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,假装打我们发给你的信息  就这样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Pretend to type the information we pass you. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.75,2:30:59.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿是东京广播电台 孤儿安妮开始播音\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is Orphan Annie from Radio Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.25,2:31:01.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,南太平洋上孤独的小伙子们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To all the lonely boys in the South Pacific...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:02.09,2:31:04.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,小心  敌人会找上你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}watch out... the enemy will get you.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:04.39,2:31:05.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也许她说的对\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe she's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:10.63,2:31:13.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本人在发报!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Japs transmitting!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:14.03,2:31:17.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  雷达发现距离四百码处有日本巡逻艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, radar reports Japanese patrol boats. Range 400 yards.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.84,2:31:20.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,多远? 四百码  正在靠近  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How many yards? 400 yards and closing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.11,2:31:22.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,理查兹  快  日军逼近  快走\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Richards, Japs! 400 yards! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.91,2:31:25.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,哈尔西将军命令巡洋舰开火\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Admiral Halsey's ordering the cruisers to open fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.98,2:31:28.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本巡逻艇可能会报告我们的位置\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We gotta sink these Jap boats before they give us away.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:29.01,2:31:30.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,全体人员就位\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go to general quarters!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:30.15,2:31:32.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快  快\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.65,2:31:34.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:36.69,2:31:37.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,情况不妙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This can't be good!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.03,2:31:47.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,日本人距离一海里  正在报告我们的位置\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Japs one mile away. They reported our position.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:47.60,2:31:50.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,预定起飞点在四百海里处  现在还有多远\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Supposed to launch 400 miles away. How far are we now?
