Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.62,2:32:11.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,陆军飞行员  立即就位!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Army pilots! Man your planes! Man your planes!
