Dialogue: 0,2:32:51.53,2:32:53.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,动作快点\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go! Move!
